#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn131:11.1"
msgid "‘Bhaddekarattassa vo, bhikkhave, uddesañca vibhaṅgañca desessāmī’ti—"
msgstr ""
"And that’s what I meant when I said: ‘I shall teach you the passage for "
"recitation and the analysis of One Fine Night.’”"

msgctxt "mn131:11.2"
msgid "iti yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ idametaṃ paṭicca vuttan”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn131:11.3"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn131:11.4"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn131:11.5"
msgid "Bhaddekarattasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
